{"tid":490607,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"150身家幫美女司機 露宿漢獲逾300萬捐款改寫人生","createTime":"2017-12-05T19:01:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-06T16:36:17.000Z","uid":22675,"like":75,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"8a6b6e510dc5f57a93e7513d6ec10d110fa86645","tid":490607,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T19:01:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171205/large/1512439825_f978.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171205%2Flarge%2F1512439825_f978.jpg&h=dbc2411b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n即時國際  2017-12-05 11:03:04 HKT\t <br />\n         <br />\n<br />\n美國新澤西州一名女子曾受一名露宿者恩惠，為報恩在網上為對方籌募生活費，怎料反應異常踴躍，成功籌得近40萬美元(312萬港元)讓他生活重回正軌，她感激大眾的慷慨，現打算成立基金，並將多餘的善款捐出。<br />\n<br />\n任職新澤西交通部、27歲的麥克盧爾（Kate McClure）上月10日為34歲露宿者博比特（Johnny Bobbitt Jr.）成立籌款專頁，她現解釋會如何運作捐款，「首要是覓得住所，是博比特擁有的！！他永不會再擔心沒有瓦遮頭！！第二是他會買夢寐以求的汽車&hellip;&hellip;他一直想要1999年的Ford Ranger」。<br />\n<br />\n麥克盧爾指會以博比特的名義成立基金，及設立戶口以資助他日常生活需要，直至他找到工作，最後將餘下的錢捐給曾為他伸出援手的機構或人。<br />\n<br />\n麥克盧爾有天駕車，駛至費城95號州際公路時汽油耗盡拋錨，她當時正要摸黑走到油站，幸遇上博比特，他便着她返回車內等候，他用身上僅有的20美元（156港元）行了數條街為她買油，令她非常感動。"},{"pid":"dd31b4ed4cd2eb40751857e4dd48d08fba9976b1","tid":490607,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T19:02:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20171205/57542347\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171205%2F57542347&d=3%2F5YkPlJbG%2BQjCW%2B8PjjmUzHknCl6yzZyFDyfiap5zU%3D&h=ebed2313\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171205%2F57542347&h=9f732617\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20171205/57542347</a>"},{"pid":"849c1a1d2c322a63830e353ebd264c309619a491","tid":490607,"uid":7862